                "subtype": "heightened",
                "level": 7,
                "text": "The fire damage increases to 3d6, and the persistent fire damage increases to 3d4. If the target gets a critical success on a Demoralize check using Performance, the target of the Demoralize check becomes fleeing from the target of *flame dancer* for 1 round.",
